data.description: Welcome home to this cozy 2 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home in the heart of Fort Mill.  Upon entering, you will be greeted by an open floor plan & an inviting gas log fireplace.  The kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances and an abundance of cabinet space!  There are TWO bedrooms on the second level, each with their own full bath.   Outside is a private, fenced back patio with space for seating and grilling out.  You can walk everywhere in this community . . . several grocery stores and the gym are close by!  Affordable monthly HOA fees include the community pool and playground.  Very convenient to shopping and dining as well as top-rated Fort Mill Schools.
